cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is about optimizing convolutional neural networks for low-power devices, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a novel approach for restructuring convolutional kernels, which could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the reduction of parameters and calculations, which could be related to data structures (cs.DS).
